product.name: Floor Mats for Tesla Model Y 2021-2024, Set of 6 Mats All Weather TPE Waterproof Anti-Slip Front & Rear Trunk Mats Cargo Liners, Custom Fit for Tesla 5-Seater (Not Fit 7-Seat)
product.description:
These Model Y floor mats provide exceptional protection for your Model Y's interior, safeguarding the original carpeting against spills, dirt, and wear and tear.These Model Y Floor Mats are custom-fit, ensuring a precise and secure placement that doesn't interfere with pedals or safety features.
NOTE: PLEASE REMOVE THE OLD CARPET MATS OR FLOOR MATS BEFORE INSTALLING OUR NEW FLOOR MATS.
1x Driver Side Mat
1x Passenger Side Mat
1x Rear Seat Mat
1x Front Trunk Mat
1x Rear Trunk Mat
1x Rear Trunk Storage Mat
product.bullet_points:
• PERFECT FIT - Size：31.9*22.8*9.45inch Model Y all weather floor mats set are made specifically for your 2021-2024 Tesla Model Y. Our 3D tech ensures a perfect fit on your vehicle, and our raised grip technology ensures they stay in place. Fit 2021-2024 2025 Y Model 5-seat Only
• Premium Material - The all weather floor mat compatible with Tesla Model Y accessories 2022 is made of eco-friendly TPE materials, which are non-toxic and safe for both humans and the environment, aging resistance and oil resistance, scratch resistance, odorless and can be recycled.
• Full Protection - The floor mat set compatible with Tesla Model Y accessories 2023 provides full coverage to keep your car away from sewage, dust, hair and other debris. The non-slip textured design keeps them firmly in place on the floor and in the trunk, and the high edgee design prevents sewage from running out and dirtying the floor.
• DURABLE AND WATERPROOF - Floor Mats are waterproof, stain resistant, durable, and easy to clean. Easily clean with a paper towel, or remove them from your car to hose them down with water. Non slip, ultra grip technology, ensuring your mats stay in place! We provide the best Tesla Model Y
• What You Received - There are 6pcs set - 1pcs front trunk mat, 3pcs floor mat, 1pcs trunk mat and 1pcs rear storage trunk mat included in a well-packed box. Please feel free to contact us if you have any questions.
